name: Kasa UI Kit - Demo version
description:
Kasa UI Kit for Figma is a pack of high-quality screen templates and a set of UI elements that will help you to design or prototype a house rental-related app project.


Features

  • 30+ High quality screens
  • 40+ Variant based components
  • Well organized and layered
  • Custom illustrations and icons included
  • Global color scheme
  • Typography system
  • Based on 375x812px resolution (iPhone 11 Pro / X)
